constituent: year end, stop, footprint, one, little, small, march
heisigStory: Stop . . . march . . . little. Be sure not to forget that final dot in the element for march.
hint: Santa had to put his foot down to stop a march of little guys, namely elves. They were protesting the harsh treatment they get every year-end when Santa asks them to step up toy production for the holiday season.

koohiiStory2: At the year-end, everything seems to come to a stop. However, there´s still enough time for a little march to celebrate.
